    User[Client / User<br/>Owner or Driver] -->|Upload load PDF / expense receipt| WebApp[Main App<br/>Web Interface]

    WebApp -->|Send request to backend API| Backend[Backend App<br/>Business Logic + APIs]

    Backend -->|Send PDF for extraction| PDFProcessor[PDF Processor<br/>OCR + Data Extraction]

    PDFProcessor -->|Return extracted load / expense data| Backend

    Backend -->|Save extracted data| DB[(Database)]

    Backend -->|Fetch saved loads, expenses, profit data| DB

    Backend -->|Return response| WebApp

    WebApp -->|Show extracted info / status / profit| User